<HR>
<H1 ALIGN="CENTER">Internet Legal Resources for Attorneys</H1>
<H2 ALIGN="CENTER">by Bradley A. Slutsky</H2>
<HR>
<CENTER><B>Index</B></CENTER>
<DL><DT><a href="#1.">E-Mail</a>
<DT><a href="#2.">ListServ Discussion Groups</a>
<DT><a href="#3.">Usenet Newsgroups</a>
