<CENTER><IMG SRC="/gif/k-s2b.gif"></CENTER>
<CENTER><HR>
<h1>General Commercial Litigation Practice</h1>
</CENTER>
<p>
King &amp; Spalding has a significant General Commercial Litigation Practice, with extensive trial experience in commercial disputes in forums throughout the United States.  Over the past 10 years, the Firm has represented some of America's leading companies, professional corporations and firms in substantial commercial litigation in state and federal courts across the country. <p>

The Commercial Litigation Practice includes numerous lawyers experienced in complex business dispute litigation involving issues such as alleged commercial fraud, contracts, securities, RICO, corporate governance, fiduciary duties, antitrust, lender liability, professional liability, tax, and construction matters.  This Group also has considerable experience in conducting corporate investigations in a variety of contexts, including internal and independent litigation committee investigations. <p>
<p>
