<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Canadian Centre on Substance Abuse, CCSA, addictions, drugs, alcohol</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY>
<IMG SRC="/newlogo.gif" ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=372 HEIGHT=167 ALT="CCSA-CCLAT">
<BR CLEAR=left><BR><P>
<FONT SIZE=6>Canadian Centre on Substance Abuse<FONT SIZE=4> is a <A HREF="/funding.htm#funding">non-profit organization</A> working to minimize the harm associated with the use of 
alcohol, tobacco and other drugs.  The Centre was created in 1988 under <A HREF="/cds.htm">Canada's Drug Strategy</A>.  To find out how you can support Canadian efforts to treat and prevent substance abuse problems, <A HREF="/funding.htm#support">click here.</A><FONT SIZE=3>
