<H4><A HREF="/cp96intr.htm">Preview of Canadian Profile 1996</A></H4>
<B>FASLINK<BR>An FAS/FAE listserv is now available.  FASLINK provides an electronic forum for the discussion of 
FAS/FAE issues. Topics addressed to date have included, for example, conference announcements, new 
research, and alternative therapies. Those interested in joining the list should send an email message to 
<B>list@ccsa.ca</B> and type: <B>join faslink</B>, in the body of the message (using lowercase letters). </B><P>
