<TITLE>CSAIN, Canadian Substance Abuse Information Network</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="csain1.gif" ALT="CSAIN:  Canadian Substance Abuse Information Network"><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=3 COLOR=0000FF>CSAIN is a consortium of the major libraries and resource centres that disseminate substance abuse and addictions information in Canada. Members exchange information, refer information requests to one another, and contribute to national information products.<P>
As extensive information on ATOD issues is available elsewhere at this site, this page will provide general information of interest to librarians and information specialists, not necessarily focussed on substance abuse issues.</FONT><BR CLEAR=LEFT><P><P>
<I>last update 96/12/10</I><P><P>
