<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>National Clearinghouse on Substance Abuse</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR=#a8a8a8>
<FONT COLOR=#ffffff><H1>Problem Gambling Listserv</H1></FONT>
<IMG SRC="/ccsa2.gif" WIDTH=574 HEIGHT=20><P><P>
As opportunities to engage in various forms of gaming have increased in Canada and elsewhere, interest in problems associated with gambling has also increased.  A new listserv has been created by the Canadian Centre on Substance Abuse to support information exchange among those interested in addressing problem gambling through research, prevention, treatment and policy development activity.  Comments, suggestions or inquiries concerning the listserv are welcome and can be directed to Gary Roberts: <A HREF ="mailto:groberts@ccsa.ca">groberts@ccsa.ca</A>.<P>
To join the list send an email message to <A HREF="mailto:list@ccsa.ca">list@ccsa.ca</A><BR>
and in the body of the message type (in lower-case letters):<BR>
<STRONG>join prob_gamb</STRONG><P>
