revenue
<LI>Tobacco sales dropped 37% from 1981-91, but smoking still kills over 35,000 Canadians annually
<LI>Over 1 million Canadians (5% of the population) smoke marijuana or hashish
<LI>Over 56,000 illicit drug offences were committed in 1991
</UL>
