http://www.ccsa.ca:80/horiz2e.htm 199.126.12.34 19961231213231 text/html 7079
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 31-Dec-96 21:42:46 GMT
