<DOCNO>WT06-B35-198</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA003-000021-B046-375</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ccsa.ca:80/horiz3e.htm 199.126.12.34 19961231213244 text/html 8368
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 31-Dec-96 21:42:58 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 22-Nov-96 16:56:42 GMT
