http://www.ccsa.ca:80/costhigh.htm 199.126.12.34 19961231213335 text/html 44460
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 31-Dec-96 21:43:37 GMT
