<TITLE>Substance abuse policy in Canada - Presentation to the House Standing Committee on Health</TITLE>
<BODY>
<CENTER><H1>Substance Abuse Policy in 
Canada</H1>
<H2>A presentation to the House Standing 
Committee on Health</H2>
<H3>October 8, 1996</H3></CENTER>
<HR>
